Q30. Write a Java Script Program to print Fibonacci numbers on onclick event.

Answer:::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::
<html>
<head>
<script>function validate()
{
var a=document.getElementById("no").value;
var n1=0,n2=1,i,c;
for(i=1;i<=a;i++)
{
document.write(n1+" ");
c=n1+n2;
n1=n2;
n2=c;
}
}
</script>
</head>
<body>
Enter num:<input type="text" id="no"><br>
<input type="button" value="submit" onclick="validate()">
</body>
</html>
